virtual AKRESULT AK::IAkPlugin::Reset (  )  [pure virtual, inherited]

The reset action should perform any actions required to reinitialize the state of the plug-in to its original state (e.g. after Init() or on effect bypass).

Returns:
AK_Success if successful, AK_Fail otherwise.
